name: sfchronicle
text: A COVID-19 vaccine developed by Oxford and AstraZeneca shows 95% efficacy and 100% effectiveness in preventing severe illness, Astra Zeneca’s CEO reportedly said. Officials in the U.K. are expected to approve the vaccine in the coming days. https://t.co/VmWqfFQhD3

text:
Some major hospital systems in California postponed elective procedures as the influx of COVID-19 patients stressed resources and raised fears that a further surge could arrive after the holidays.

Story by @TatianaYSanchez: https://t.co/VTADYj3IBq
